    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Planning Your Project\r\n\r\nUse this chatbot to help you with **brainstorming** your pixel image, **decomposing** your image into parts, or **debugging** your code.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n- Tell the chatbot what you want to accomplish. \r\n- Ask it to help you brainstorm, decompose, or debug, see examples below.\r\n\r\n**Example Prompts:**\r\n- **Brainstorm:** I want to create an image that represents me as a **musician**. Help me come up three images I could use to represent my identity.\r\n- **Debug:** My `turn_right` function isn't working. Help me debug it: \r\n```def turn_right():\r\n    turn_left()\r\n    turn_left()\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Tips**:\r\n- To get more ideas, simply ask the chatbot to **\"Come up with 3 more ideas\"**\r\n- If the chatbot's debugging advice is not useful, try prompting it to debug one line of code or code chunk at a time. ",
